=====================================================================================================================

	jsp페이지 작성
	
	- 가장 상단 : <%@ include file="setting.jsp" %>
	
	- 메뉴 : <%@ include file ="../Template/top.jsp" %>
	- 하단 : <%@ include file ="../Template/footer.jsp" %>

=====================================================================================================================

	jsp파일 생성 위치
	대메뉴>중메뉴>소메뉴
	ex)
	mypage일 경우
	user -> mypage -> mypage.jsp
	search일 경우
	common -> search -> search.jsp

=====================================================================================================================

	Controller, Service, DAO, mappers
	작성시 _자기이름이니셜 붙이기
	ex)
	Controller_syk
	Service_syk
	DAO_syk
	mapper_syk

=====================================================================================================================
	
	-servlet-context 
	<beans:property name="jndiName" value="java:comp/env/jdbc/Oracle11g" />
	현재는 Oracle11g로 되어있으나, 바뀔 예정
	
=====================================================================================================================

